{"tid":2117587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄：2020年對學生是困難一年　惟辦法比困難多","createTime":"2020-07-21T03:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T04:27:46.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6feef14eea80e920b5f71e8e90883242b1d2b4fe","tid":2117587,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T03:08:08.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>DSE 嘅考生入嚟一人一句多謝楊局長 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中學文憑試明日放榜，因疫情關係，學校以電子方式向考生派發成績通知書。教育局局長楊潤雄在社交專頁表示，過往他都會親自到學校為學生打氣，但今年為減少人群聚集，決定轉為拍片在網上為考生打氣。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，<strong>2020年對全港學生而言是困難的一年，曾因疫情而停課，打亂部分同學學習及準備功夫</strong>，文憑試亦延遲開考，但在這個情況下更能體會「辦法總比困難多」，總有辦法克服疫情和其他困難。楊潤雄說，目前本地專上課程多元化，有足夠學位，無論考生成績如何都會找到升學途徑，他寄語考生腳踏實地，一步一腳印。他又強調，儘管世事多變，市民支持應屆考生的真心仍然不變。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538989-20200721.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538989-20200721.htm&d=bKbBxrmwQkzC5eAvTqWhP6wVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=4dd3214d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538989-20200721.htm&h=522c768d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538989-20200721.htm</a>"},{"pid":"537391f78d84442264fe47de23d8aeceeca14b44","tid":2117587,"uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T03:09:16.000Z","msg":"無懼世事變改 還是越難越愛？"},{"pid":"5b58f41dfeba3d0e3cc3f236fc72b264a395c299","tid":2117587,"uid":7323,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啊"},{"pid":"417aa5d9e064de894ef96da819558ddb88f96610","tid":2117587,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58ddd3d0f5b240992aed